1a20ab2d-ee70-4fe1-9b6d-e86050facb38.summary: Set in the fictional world of Azeroth, WoW allows players to create avatar-style characters and explore a sprawling universe while interacting with nonreal players—called nonplayer characters (NPCs)—and other real-world players (PCs)

d9f1e8bf-55fd-410a-9e1e-634be71a2dce.title: League of Legends
d9f1e8bf-55fd-410a-9e1e-634be71a2dce.summary: League of Legends is a team-based strategy game where two teams of five powerful champions face off to destroy the other's base. Choose from over 140 champions to make epic plays, secure kills, and take down towers as you battle your way to victory.
